case.name: Clutch Case
notes: Tier OddsWeights Use The Project Default Distribution (Blue/Purple/Pink/Red/Gold).
Within Each Tier, Item Weights Are Split Equally With Any Remainder Assigned To The First Items In Order; StatTrak Is Applied At 10% (Rounded) For Weapons, And Disabled For Gloves.
